{"type":"message","id":"25c8846b","parentId":"7e3c4588","timestamp":"2026-03-03T23:02:11.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've successfully posted the Google Education news summary to the Discord channel. Let me summarize what I accomplished.","thinkingSignature":"566a1480116ae1dfc548557dc31193156872dbbe78bddc54cca957fd0c0e89b7"},{"type":"text","text":"已完成 Google Education 新聞摘要並發布至 Discord 頻道。\n\n**收集的新聞重點：**\n1. **2025年度回顧** - Gemini for Education 已進入超過1,000所美國大學，節省教師時間\n2. **課堂 AI 工具** - 推出30+種 Gemini AI 工具，免費提供教育機構使用\n3. **2025開學新方案** - 為多國學生提供免費 AI Pro 訂閱\n\n所有新聞已按照要求的格式（標題、100字簡介、網址）發布到 Discord 頻道。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":13234,"output":153,"cacheRead":10295,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23682,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772578924438}}
